{"tid":1712094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有youtuber教大家整槍","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T00:44:04.000Z","uid":280783,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24c3b8a95d0e2cde44fe46a2b9c8289256820227","tid":1712094,"uid":280783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"要狗賊血債血償方法有三<br />\n一,<br />\n跟youtuber學野<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jaHEr2yr6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3jaHEr2yr6s&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7V3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=5ab6e187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3jaHEr2yr6s</a><br />\n更多詳情: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1608315/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1608315/page/1</a><br />\n更多更多詳情來自其他巴打既天神手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1711378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1711378</a><br />\n<br />\n二,<br />\n刺蝟戰術<br />\n狗好鐘意濫捕，如果佢捕食著隻刺蝟會點?<br />\n尤其是小狗三四隻行動既時間 刺蝟根本唔洗驚 狗一埋黎就出刺<br />\n發揮刺蝟既近身優點 刺蝟近身有優勢都唔會主動出擊<br />\n所以近身唔一定要主動出擊，引狗埋黎咬都一樣<br />\n引去暗角出刺又得 轉角出刺都得 埋伏出刺亦得<br />\n如果D狗捕食期間唔小心被刺吉死左自己 仲有意外裝備收穫<br />\n<br />\n三,<br />\n蠻牛 / 戰馬 戰術<br />\n戰馬係咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.trendsmap.com/twitter/tweet/1193692366277709824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trendsmap.com%2Ftwitter%2Ftweet%2F1193692366277709824&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7V3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=f746b44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.trendsmap.com/twitter/tweet/1193692366277709824</a><br />\n咁蠻牛又係咩?"},{"pid":"d0438e81a36a073dd650beec14a639c372223316","tid":1712094,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗<br />\n❗H2SO4❗"},{"pid":"a6976a861eb2367bba38937de3672f31431f9469","tid":1712094,"uid":312242,"like":